name: SuperHobo Kills Wonderland
description:
SuperHobo is triping again! Help him save reality from his own imagination.

But be careful ! Your magic PewPew gun can still hurt real people and SuperHobo eyesight is not what it used to be.

You will have to get close enought to see what's real and what's not.

Game made in 7 days for the Brackeys Game Jam 2022.1.
